{"word":"συναναιρέω","slug":"συναναιρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συναναιρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ήσω</el>) (aor2 <el>-ανεῖλον</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to destroy together with</i>, <el>τινά τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to destroy altogether</i> or <i>utterly</i>, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to give the same answer</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}